latestIgtvVideos.title: White dress stained
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A song that me and @surana_shetty wrote randomly one night about broken love and what it can do to people 
Hope you like it 

Lyrics : Sufi 
Melody : Sufi and Surana 
Production and singing : Surana 

—————————————————
Feeling the same thing 
Same routine up and down again 
My devils are bored cause their ain’t no fun game 
Ghost in the mirror 
The centre of my pain 
Can’t let go of it 
Like I couldn’t let go of him 

But I never knew why cause he brought me the high 
Then kept me aside like a forgotten toy 
So I sit there and hide 
Pretending I’m fine 
Cause even the moon knows I’m lying 

If nothing this chaos taught me one thing 
No matter how hard you try 
You’ll always realise 
That loves nothing but a white dress stained 

Remember 4th of July the time of our lives 
How we had our first kiss under the flickering lights 
Now I’m here tonight and I’m dead inside 
But it’s still better cause you’re the one who died 

So I picked up the knife 
I don’t know why 
It was just a high and now I say goodbye 
Now I sit here and smile no hiding tonight 
Cause only the moon knows my crimes 

If nothing this chaos taught me one thing 
No matter how hard i try 
I’ve come to find 
Our love was always meant to die 

You believe in eye for an eye 
But not heart for heart 
That’s why you left with mine 
With you It’s me myself and I 

If nothing this chaos taught me one thing 
People always die from the strokes of time 
Only this time the hands are mine 

Much love xoxo 

#music #taylorswift #folklore #song #poetry
